snippet.title: Miss Paint Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist here! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2755990/Miss_Paint/

An editable platformer! Use paint program edit tools to transform levels to lead Miss Paint to victory in this simple but deep puzzle game!

Originally made for Bigmode Game Jam 2023
For more updates follow us on Twitter - https://twitter.com/TwiceTwiceStu
